<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Good to see council tax exemption being introduced for care experienced young people across Scotland from April 2018. Sensible move for corporate parents. <a href="/COSLA" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="36039937"><s>@</s><b>COSLA</b></a> <a href="/COSLA_CYP" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="761139119431028736"><s>@</s><b>COSLA_CYP</b></a> <a href="/hashtag/YOYP2018?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>YOYP2018</b></a> <a href="/whocaresscot" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="851114790"><s>@</s><b>whocaresscot</b></a><a href="https://t.co/SCiYVaHFog" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/cllrdgibson/status/963924923122159616" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/cllrdgibson/status/963924923122159616"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/cllrdgibson/st</span><span class="invisible">atus/963924923122159616</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Horrible news for staff and communities affected. I had my first bank account in Bannockburn branch of <a href="/RBS" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="429724798"><s>@</s><b>RBS</b></a> when I was at primary school and still have a relationship with them today. Might need to rethink that. UK Government owns <a href="/hashtag/rbs?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>rbs</b></a> and could choose to do things differently.<a href="https://t.co/SmsBOrK4zz" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/LabourStirling/status/936653331258331136" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/LabourStirling/status/936653331258331136"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/LabourStirling</span><span class="invisible">/status/936653331258331136</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

  </div>
  <ul>

    <div class="QuoteTweet-innerContainer u-cf js-permalink js-media-container" data-item-id="841333614285602822" data-item-type="tweet" data-screen-name="BBCArchive" data-user-id="51023770" href="/BBCArchive/status/841333614285602822" data-conversation-id="841333614285602822" tabindex="0">

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">I'm working hard in <a href="/hashtag/stirlingeast?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>stirlingeast</b></a> to put green community led energy schemes in the spotlight. Communities don't need the risks of <a href="/hashtag/fracking?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>fracking</b></a><a href="https://t.co/cKUYRhhdDD" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/LabourStirling/status/846993396447264768" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/LabourStirling/status/846993396447264768"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/LabourStirling</span><span class="invisible">/status/846993396447264768</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

  <div class="dropdown-menu is-autoCentered">
  <div class="dropdown-caret">
    <div class="caret-outer"></div>
    <div class="caret-inner"></div>

  <ul>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">well worth a read - cuts to the heart of what is wrong both with local authority funding and Scot.     <script nonce="" id="track-ttft-body-script">
  if(window.ttft){
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('page', document.getElementById('swift-page-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('section', document.getElementById('swift-section-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('client_record_time', window.ttft.now());
  }
